data.description: You will not believe just how spacious and fantastic the floorplan for this beautiful 2bed/2bath condo is. There's plenty of natural light.  You will will be in awe by the beauty of this building as soon as you walk in.  It's immaculate, clean and well maintained.  Storage in basement, and elevator.  There are parking/ garage space option nearby for rent.  Security cameras surround the building, secured front and back entry. Other features include cherry hardwood flooring, sliding door that leads to balcony, high ceiling, maple cabinets with black granite countertops, washer and dryer.  It is located at the perfect location.  Steps away from grocery shopping, gym, restaurants and CTA bus routes.  Minutes away from the train transportations, Metra, and the Lakefront.  In building amazon hub.  You ask for it and this unit has it to offer!
